  "text": "Well, our continued communication with Ra beautiful to the physical energies of the instrument. I and we may answer in two modes. Firstly, if the instrument were thusly dedicated to this use, with no transfer of energy of a physical complex nature, it would begin to call upon the vital energy itself, and this done in any substantive measure is actively deleterious to a mind, a body, spirit, complex, if that complex wishes further experience in the illusion which it now distorts. Secondly, if care is taken, firstly to monitor the outer parameters of the instrument, then to a transfer of physical energy by a sexual transfer, by a magical, a protection, and lastly, by the energetic displacements of a thought forms energizing the instrument enduring contact, there is no difficulty in that there is no worsening of the instruments mind, a body, a spirit, complex and distortions of a strength, a weakness, it is to be noted that the instrument by dedicating itself to this service attracts greetings of which you are aware these are inconvenient, but with care taken need not be lastingly deleterious either to the instrument or the contact.",
